{"tid":433976,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攞住特區護照加英國簽證 去英國讀書要七天內俾34鎊去警署報到","createTime":"2017-10-13T00:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T00:56:35.000Z","uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b7643631525e78aee22cd5071b97f5afaa8647f3","tid":433976,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:28:56.000Z","msg":"攞住特區護照加 英國簽證 去讀書點解要俾34鎊做警署報到<br />\n<br />\n2017-07-27&nbsp;/ by&nbsp;martinoei 黃世澤<br />\n<br />\n好多香港啲廢老，大中華膠上腦，無幫子女申請BNO，送子女揸 英國簽證 去英國留學就中招。如果讀碩士，BNO仲可以用Tier-5 YMS Visa隨時走得，<span style=\"color: red;\">特區護照就慢慢同成棚中國人困獸鬥，仲要揸特區護照，係要七天內警署報到</span>。好多人唔明， 英國簽證 持有人要去警署報到係乜意思。<br />\n<br />\n英國簽證 持有人去警署報到嘅意義<br />\n<br />\n大部分國籍都唔駛去警署報到，包括BNO，但如果你持係以下國籍嘅證件，而無持BNO或其他唔駛警察報到國家證件，或者你無行使EEA Family Rights，唔該你去一去，包括：<br />\n<br />\n阿富汗阿爾巴尼亞阿根廷亞美尼亞亞塞拜疆巴林白俄羅斯玻利維亞巴西中國哥倫比亞古巴埃及格魯吉亞伊朗伊拉克以色列約旦哈薩克科威特吉爾吉斯黎巴嫩利比亞摩爾多瓦摩洛哥北韓阿曼巴勒斯坦秘魯卡塔爾俄羅斯沙地阿拉伯蘇丹敘利亞塔吉克突尼斯土耳其土庫曼阿拉伯聯合酋長國烏克蘭烏茲別克也門<br />\n<br />\n呢堆國家，簡單嚟講，不外乎以下幾種　<br />\n<br />\n回教國家，有可能涉及恐怖主義行為，差唔多大部分回教國家都涵蓋前蘇聯加盟共和國又未入歐盟，好多都涉及俄國間諜活動本身有亂咁老笠人地國家國民嘅紀錄，北韓同以色列都係呢隻間諜活動太過離譜，俄國同中國都係呢類<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/15467/%E6%94%9E%E4%BD%8F%E7%89%B9%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B7%E7%85%A7%E5%8A%A0-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89-%E5%8E%BB%E8%AE%80%E6%9B%B8%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E8%A6%81%E4%BF%BE34%E9%8E%8A%E5%81%9A%E8%AD%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F15467%2F%25E6%2594%259E%25E4%25BD%258F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E7%2585%25A7%25E5%258A%25A0-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E5%258E%25BB%25E8%25AE%2580%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BF%25BE34%25E9%258E%258A%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%25AD%25A6&d=88pLlQRtdcCMvbw0s3jR4lKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=1372154e\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/15467/%E6%94%9E%E4%BD%8F%E7%89%B9%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B7%E7%85%A7%E5%8A%A0-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89-%E5%8E%BB%E8%AE%80%E6%9B%B8%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E8%A6%81%E4%BF%BE34%E9%8E%8A%E5%81%9A%E8%AD%A6</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/immigration-rules\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fguidance%2Fimmigration-rules&d=88pLlQRtdcCMvbw0s3jR4lKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=d647a8c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/guidance/immigration-rules</a><br />\n中國包括香港及澳門<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.southyorks.police.uk/overseasvisitors\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.southyorks.police.uk%2Foverseasvisitors&d=88pLlQRtdcCMvbw0s3jR4lKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=d60db53c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.southyorks.police.uk/overseasvisitors</a>"},{"pid":"071f9749e9ad2e1ff223ada7b042089b67018287","tid":433976,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9cc8c25cd8574aad83c8ee28897744904b6e03","tid":433976,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5483df8e6a6c4c910e184ad4ad2a0428f2f720","tid":433976,"uid":77453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:41:52.000Z","msg":"共享中國人榮耀 當然要報到磅水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252b358f62e3a3be15b68634bff4c5b3b117303e","tid":433976,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:44:12.000Z","msg":"有得揀梗係攞bno"},{"pid":"67be357d79b72ee4de1931764075901c40988fac","tid":433976,"uid":59929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:45:43.000Z","msg":"而家去英國讀書好多都九七後出世 點會仲有 bno <br />\n夠知阿媽係女人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb8d3c7856175a20214897bc1be60760d3bdf04","tid":433976,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:50:19.000Z","msg":"stay 6個月或以上都要